{"tid":1705843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫] 點樣善用兄弟爬山+不指責","createTime":"2019-11-11T02:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:57:36.000Z","uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21e19ebf17ea2deb547de212691a407eb1cef92a","tid":1705843,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"先鳴謝手足既post<br />\n<blockquote>點解有啲人屌極都唔醒? 媽，好多負能量呀!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dQHBdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dQHBdS</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抗爭現疲態 正常<br />\n其中一個現象: <br />\n<strong>忘記宗旨 -&gt; 付出多 <span style=\"color: red;\">屌</span> 付出少</strong><br />\n<br />\n親身參與者 有情緒好正常 睇唔過眼咪屌<br />\n但抗爭 從來都係犠牲<br />\n偉大+悟性高 =&gt; 付出多<br />\n反相 未夠信心衝破心理關口 就付出少<br />\n<strong>唔會被屌醒就變付出多</strong> <br />\n只會灰機 &quot;已經付出咗仲要被你屌&quot; =&gt; <strong>愈黎愈少人撐</strong><br />\n<br />\n想大家做多啲<br />\n轉化為 <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">付出多 <strong>鼓勵</strong> 付出少</span></span><br />\n手足就有方足有心信逐步參與多啲<br />\n<br />\n大家唔會知團結力量有幾大<br />\n兄弟爬山 直至光復香港<br />\n好嗎?"},{"pid":"3dc90fcac87acc3262b05b5633087f28380b789f","tid":1705843,"uid":99356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}